      "type": "custom-header-para",
      "name": "custom-text-para",
      "settings": {
        "heading": "IT STARTS WITH A SPARK",
        "description": "<br>At Lafoli, we know handbags are more than accessories. They are your reward, your treat yourself, the star of your closet and the piece that ties your outfit together. It’s a little luxury that sparks joy. <br>\n<br>We design remembering that feeling, following that spark wherever it leads, no questions asked. Mix that with considered aesthetic, immense attention to craftsmanship, and a touch of madness.\n<br><br>And you get Lafoli.\n Welcome to it.",
