      "settings": {
        "heading": "UNEXPECTED ALWAYS",
        "description": "<br>We love stories that pull magic out of the mundane. We believe fun can sit at the table with elegance - after all, they make each other better. For us, handbags are just way to explore that magic, that fun. And let's be honest, that's what makes life more interesting!\n<br><br>\nLet us be your cue to welcome a surprise or two, and a reminder to always leave room for the unexpected, and a bit of beautiful chaos.\n<br><br>And what can be a better reminder than something you carry every day? :)",
